<br>
What many people <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  fail</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to realise is that pets are just perma-charmed NPCs, with (nearly) all the same rules as NPCs.  The skill gain rule which applies to NPCs also applies to pets.  Pets do not cease to be NPC just because their owner is in a duel, thus you can raise skills by fighting pets.<br>
<br>
Clear now???<br>
<br>
P.S. I wasn't flaming the questioner, er se.  On the other hand, it does get frustrating handing out well known information to people who could have done a quick search and found it themselves (or even just used a little common sense). <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uusrbinperldashw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>usrbinperl dashw</A> at: 8/24/02 7:37:59 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uazixdamage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Azix Da Mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#333333>(8/24/02 10:29:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=314.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.oek.dk/~vip/image/head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: skill-up</span><hr size=1> I used to have low defense skill too, but after some pulling sessions in OS in AE groups my defense is now capped, and with DS on, my Offense went to max as well. <p><table width="100%" border="0"><tr width="25%"><td rowspan="2" width="25%" align="center"></td><td width="50%" align="center"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22508" target="new">Azix LFG</a></td><td rowspan="2" width="25%" align="center"></td></tr><tr><td height="160" align="center"><a href="http://www.nexxus.dk" target="new"><img src="http://www.oek.dk/~vip/image/sig.gif" border="0"></a></td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujochangaladar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jochan Galadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 523<br> <font color=#333333>(8/25/02 4:5